properties.description: Gathering user feedback on our new features
properties.title: Product Feedback Survey

properties.question_text: What do you like most about our product?
How would you rate your overall experience?

properties.text: The user interface is really intuitive and clean. I love how easy it is to navigate between features.
The pricing feels a bit high for small teams. Also, the mobile app could use some performance improvements.
The collaboration features are fantastic. Real-time editing works smoothly.
Need better documentation and more tutorial videos. The learning curve is steep.
Love the dark mode option and the customizable dashboard.
The pricing model is confusing. Would prefer a simpler tier structure.
Fast performance and reliable uptime. Never had any crashes.
The export functionality is limited. Need more format options like PDF and DOCX.
The integration with other tools we use is seamless. Saves us so much time.
Customer support response times could be faster. Sometimes takes days to hear back.
Great analytics dashboard with useful insights.
The mobile experience needs work. Too many features are desktop-only.
The security features give me peace of mind. Two-factor authentication works well.
Pricing is too expensive for freelancers. Need a cheaper solo plan.
The template library is extensive and saves time on setup.
The search function doesn't always return relevant results. Needs better algorithms.
Customer onboarding process was smooth and helpful.
Would love to see more customization options for reports and dashboards.
The API documentation is clear and well-organized.
The pricing seems high compared to competitors. Hard to justify the cost.
Love the notification system - keeps me updated without being intrusive.
The interface feels cluttered on smaller screens. Needs responsive design improvements.
The keyboard shortcuts make workflow much faster.
Need offline mode for when internet is unstable.
The version control feature is excellent for team collaboration.
Wish there was a free tier for students and educators.
Data visualization tools are powerful and easy to use.
The onboarding tutorial could be more interactive and engaging.
The permission controls are flexible and secure.
Performance slows down when working with large datasets.
The automation features save hours of manual work.
The pricing structure doesn't scale well for growing teams.
Import/export functionality works flawlessly.
Could use better mobile app notifications and sync.
The UI is modern and aesthetically pleasing.
Need more training resources and webinars for advanced features.
The comment and feedback system encourages good team communication.
Pricing feels unjustified given the limited features compared to alternatives.
The platform stability is impressive - rarely any downtime.
The user interface could be more intuitive for first-time users.

properties.explanation: The responses contradict each other because one response states that the user interface is intuitive and easy to navigate, while the other indicates that it lacks intuitiveness for new users, suggesting a negative experience with the same feature.

The responses contradict each other because one response highlights the user interface as intuitive and easy to use, while the other points out that it feels cluttered, indicating a negative experience. This represents a direct conflict in opinions about the same feature.

The two responses contradict each other because one indicates that the mobile app's performance is lacking and needs improvement, while the other asserts that the performance is fast and reliable, suggesting no issues at all.

The two responses contradict each other because one states that performance slows down with large datasets, suggesting a negative experience, while the other asserts that the performance is fast and reliable, indicating a positive experience. These conflicting views on performance create a contradiction.
